<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Quotation Accepted</title>
    <style>
      /* Your custom CSS styles can go here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .highlight {
        background-color: #ffff99; /* Light yellow background */
        padding: 5px;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .no-reply {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Your Quotation for Variant SKU Accepted!</h2>
      <p>Dear <span class="highlight"><%= @user.email %></span>,</p>
      <p>We are thrilled to inform you that your quotation for the variant of SKU <span class="highlight"><%= @variant_sku %></span> has been accepted! ðŸŽ‰</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing to shop with us on Spree Platform. We truly appreciate your trust in our services and products.</p>
      <p>Should you have any questions, feedback, or need assistance with anything, please don't hesitate to reach out to our dedicated Spree Admin team at <span class="highlight"><%= @spree_admin_email %></span>. We are here to ensure your shopping experience remains seamless and delightful.</p>
      <p>Once again, congratulations on your accepted quotation! We look forward to continuing to serve you and providing you with the best shopping experience possible.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      Spree Team<br>
